name: Bench Press
instructions: Lie flat on bench with feet on floor
Grip bar slightly wider than shoulder-width
Lower bar to chest with control

name: Dumbbell Press
instructions: Lie on flat bench holding dumbbells
Press dumbbells up until arms are extended
Lower with control to chest level

name: Push-ups
instructions: Lower body until chest nearly touches floor
Push back up to starting position

name: Chest Fly
instructions: Lie on bench with dumbbells extended above chest
Bring weights back together above chest

name: Dips
instructions: Push back up to starting position

name: Pull-ups
instructions: Hang from bar with palms facing away
Pull body up until chin clears bar

name: Chin-ups
instructions: Hang from bar with palms facing you

name: Bent-Over Row
instructions: Bend at hips with slight knee bend
Pull bar to lower chest/upper abdomen

name: Deadlift
instructions: Bend at hips and knees to grip bar

name: Romanian Deadlift
instructions: Hold bar with slight knee bend

name: Squat
instructions: Bar on upper back, feet shoulder-width
Lower by bending hips and knees
Descend until thighs parallel to floor
Keep chest up and core tight

name: Leg Press
instructions: Press through heels to extend legs

name: Lunges
instructions: Push through front heel to return

name: Leg Curl
instructions: Lie face down on leg curl machine

name: Front Raise
instructions: Hold dumbbells in front of thighs

name: Face Pull
instructions: Squeeze rear delts and upper back

name: Tricep Dip
instructions: Support body on bench or bars

name: Russian Twist
instructions: Sit with knees bent, lean back

name: Leg Raises
instructions: Keep lower back pressed to floor

name: Quad Stretch
instructions: Stand and pull heel to glute

name: Hamstring Stretch
instructions: Feel stretch in back of thigh

name: Glute Stretch
instructions: Cross one ankle over opposite knee

name: Hip Flexor Stretch
instructions: Feel stretch in front of hip

name: Shoulder Stretch
instructions: Use other arm to pull gently

name: Tricep Stretch
instructions: Use other hand to pull elbow

name: Lat Stretch
instructions: Feel stretch in side of back

name: Neck Stretch
instructions: Feel stretch in side of neck

name: Wrist Stretch
instructions: Pull fingers back with other hand

name: Butterfly Stretch
instructions: Sit with soles of feet together

name: Cobra Stretch
instructions: Feel stretch in front of body

name: Sit-ups
instructions: Lie on back with knees bent
Place hands behind head or crossed on chest

name: Handstand
instructions: Kick one leg up, then the other
Balance on hands with body straight

name: Running
instructions: Gradually increase pace to running speed
